1
00:01:14,157 --> 00:01:19,246
<i>Once upon a time</i>
<i>there lived a bamboo cutter.</i>

2
00:01:21,790 --> 00:01:24,501
<i>On the mountain, he would cut bamboo</i>

3
00:01:24,793 --> 00:01:27,379
<i>to make all manner of things.</i>

4
00:01:29,965 --> 00:01:33,969
<i>Sanuki no Miyatsuko was his name.</i>

5
00:01:36,638 --> 00:01:42,436
<i>One day, he saw light shining</i>
<i>from a bamboo stalk.</i>

6
00:01:48,483 --> 00:01:51,320
<i>In wonder, he drew closer.</i>

7
00:01:56,491 --> 00:02:01,830
A bamboo shoot sprouting
before the plums flower?

8
00:02:09,421 --> 00:02:10,672
What's this?

9
00:02:32,569 --> 00:02:33,695
Um...

10
00:02:34,321 --> 00:02:37,908
may I ask who you might be?

11
00:03:08,438 --> 00:03:11,983
What a beautiful princess!

12
00:03:12,526 --> 00:03:17,239
Heaven must have sent her
to me as a blessing.

13
00:04:08,790 --> 00:04:10,751
Did you catch something?

14
00:04:20,719 --> 00:04:22,888
What a pretty doll!

15
00:04:22,971 --> 00:04:25,265
No, she's sleeping.

16
00:04:25,348 --> 00:04:26,475
What?

17
00:04:32,105 --> 00:04:34,024
I've been blessed.

18
00:04:34,107 --> 00:04:35,317
Blessed?

19
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:37,444
By Heaven, in the grove!

20
00:04:41,656 --> 00:04:43,116
It's me Heaven has blessed.

21
00:04:43,325 --> 00:04:45,494
I'm the one who'll raise her.

22
00:04:45,577 --> 00:04:49,206
Raise her?
She's already a beautiful princess.

23
00:04:49,289 --> 00:04:52,209
There'll be more to this than you think.

24
00:04:52,584 --> 00:04:53,418
Right?

25
00:04:59,549 --> 00:05:00,842
Give her here!

26
00:05:16,691 --> 00:05:20,111
Don't just sit there! Bring me a cloth.

27
00:05:23,615 --> 00:05:24,866
How's this?

28
00:05:28,119 --> 00:05:32,165
There, there!

29
00:05:32,249 --> 00:05:33,416
What's going on?

30
00:05:33,708 --> 00:05:36,878
She wants me to raise her.

31
00:05:39,965 --> 00:05:42,300
Get me a nice basket.

32
00:05:42,384 --> 00:05:46,972
This is very strange, you know.

33
00:05:47,180 --> 00:05:48,765
What if she's some kind of spirit?

34
00:05:48,848 --> 00:05:50,725
What does she look like?

35
00:05:50,809 --> 00:05:52,727
A baby.

36
00:05:52,811 --> 00:05:55,939
-Right!
-But just now, she was a princess!

37
00:05:56,022 --> 00:06:01,903
That was Heaven telling us
who she'll grow into.

38
00:06:01,987 --> 00:06:02,946
Really?

39
00:06:03,029 --> 00:06:07,033
So that means we must raise her properly.

40
00:06:07,117 --> 00:06:09,119
Yes! That must be it.

41
00:06:09,202 --> 00:06:10,328
Yes.

42
00:06:11,204 --> 00:06:12,872
I see!

43
00:06:12,956 --> 00:06:14,874
But who'll nurse her?

44
00:06:14,958 --> 00:06:16,585
A wet nurse.

45
00:06:16,835 --> 00:06:20,297
And the lathe turners have a new baby.

46
00:06:20,380 --> 00:06:23,383
-So this is...
-A gift.

47
00:06:25,385 --> 00:06:26,219
What's the matter?

48
00:06:40,942 --> 00:06:43,570
What are you doing?

49
00:06:45,989 --> 00:06:49,242
There, there! You must be hungry.

50
00:06:49,451 --> 00:06:50,660
What?

51
00:06:51,077 --> 00:06:54,039
She's drinking it right down.

52
00:06:55,874 --> 00:06:58,418
I've got milk!

53
00:07:25,528 --> 00:07:26,529
She laughed!

54
00:07:27,572 --> 00:07:28,782
She did!

55
00:07:29,824 --> 00:07:32,535
Suddenly, she feels heavier.

56
00:07:32,619 --> 00:07:33,828
That can't be!

57
00:07:51,012 --> 00:07:52,889
-Now what?
-She's heavier still!

58
00:07:52,973 --> 00:07:54,474
Let me see.

59
00:07:55,642 --> 00:07:58,520
She's growing really fast.

60
00:08:15,578 --> 00:08:18,498
Plum blossoms already!

61
00:08:28,675 --> 00:08:30,343
She just got heavier again!

62
00:08:30,677 --> 00:08:31,845
You see?

63
00:08:32,303 --> 00:08:34,764
Well, I'll be!

64
00:08:35,890 --> 00:08:41,563
<i>From that day on,</i>
<i>the Bamboo Cutter and his wife</i>

65
00:08:41,646 --> 00:08:44,566
<i>would raise this miraculous child</i>
<i>as their very own.</i>

66
00:09:45,794 --> 00:09:49,005
No! You can't have those yet.

67
00:09:57,013 --> 00:09:58,181
There's a baby!

68
00:09:58,264 --> 00:10:00,475
Yeah? Where?

69
00:10:01,643 --> 00:10:03,103
Don't push!

70
00:10:03,186 --> 00:10:04,312
There!

71
00:10:25,166 --> 00:10:26,876
She looked at us!

72
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:28,753
-Yeah!
-No.

73
00:10:47,147 --> 00:10:48,940
What is it?

74
00:11:04,622 --> 00:11:06,457
-Oh, my!
-Well, I'll be!

75
00:11:26,936 --> 00:11:28,313
Princess!

76
00:11:34,110 --> 00:11:34,986
She's standing!

77
00:11:38,823 --> 00:11:39,782
She's walking!

78
00:11:46,539 --> 00:11:47,957
Oh, my!

79
00:12:02,180 --> 00:12:04,307
There, there...

80
00:12:04,807 --> 00:12:06,434
She's funny!

81
00:12:06,517 --> 00:12:07,477
She walked.

82
00:12:07,560 --> 00:12:08,895
She was just crawling.

83
00:12:08,978 --> 00:12:10,313
She's growing fast!

84
00:12:10,772 --> 00:12:13,191
Like a bamboo shoot!

85
00:12:13,274 --> 00:12:15,068
That's her! Li'l Bamboo!

86
00:12:15,151 --> 00:12:16,194
Li'l Bamboo!

87
00:12:16,277 --> 00:12:17,320
Li'l Bamboo!

88
00:12:17,820 --> 00:12:20,365
Li'l Bamboo!

89
00:12:20,448 --> 00:12:23,826
She's not Li'l Bamboo! She's Princess!

90
00:12:24,202 --> 00:12:27,830
Li'l Bamboo!

91
00:12:28,122 --> 00:12:31,834
Li'l Bamboo!

92
00:12:32,210 --> 00:12:36,923
Li'l Bamboo!

93
00:12:40,802 --> 00:12:44,806
Princess! Come to me!

94
00:12:45,139 --> 00:12:47,141
Princess! Come to me!

95
00:12:47,225 --> 00:12:52,146
Princess! Come to me!

96
00:12:52,230 --> 00:12:54,899
Li'l Bamboo!

97
00:12:55,233 --> 00:12:59,153
Princess! Come to me!

98
00:12:59,612 --> 00:13:03,157
Li'l Bamboo!

99
00:13:03,574 --> 00:13:05,952
Li'l Bamboo!

100
00:13:06,035 --> 00:13:11,082
Princess! Come to me!

101
00:13:11,416 --> 00:13:14,669
Princess! Come to me!

102
00:13:14,752 --> 00:13:17,880
Princess! Come to me!

103
00:13:59,881 --> 00:14:01,758
Do you want to come?

104
00:14:22,111 --> 00:14:24,280
Bamboo shoots. That's supper.

105
00:14:24,364 --> 00:14:27,742
Supper! Bamboo shoots!

106
00:14:31,037 --> 00:14:33,623
Right! Stand back.

107
00:14:41,381 --> 00:14:42,632
There are lots!

108
00:14:42,715 --> 00:14:44,217
Yeah!

109
00:15:15,373 --> 00:15:16,416
Come here!

110
00:15:45,736 --> 00:15:48,531
You don't mess with a wild boar!

111
00:15:51,033 --> 00:15:51,993
Huh?

112
00:15:53,619 --> 00:15:57,206
You're a strange kid. You just got bigger.

113
00:15:57,290 --> 00:15:59,750
She's weird, Sutemaru.

114
00:16:00,918 --> 00:16:03,212
She's gotten bigger again!

115
00:16:03,296 --> 00:16:05,548
Like a bamboo shoot.

116
00:16:06,174 --> 00:16:08,551
-A bamboo shoot?
-Bamboo shoot! Supper!

117
00:16:09,177 --> 00:16:11,053
Bamboo shoot!

118
00:16:11,137 --> 00:16:12,847
Li'l Bamboo!

119
00:16:12,930 --> 00:16:14,348
Li'l Bamboo!

120
00:16:17,643 --> 00:16:21,522
<i>Round, round, go round</i>

121
00:16:21,606 --> 00:16:25,401
<i>Waterwheel go round</i>

122
00:16:25,485 --> 00:16:29,322
<i>Go round, and call Mr. Sun</i>

123
